</section>

<section class="hero" id="advisory-service-file">
    <div class="hero-body">
        <h4 class="title is-4 has-text-centered">諮詢及診斷紀錄</h4>
        <h5 class="subtitle is-5 has-text-centered has-text-grey has-text-weight-normal">Advisory service file</h5>
        <article class="message">
            <div class="message-header">
                <p>診斷紀錄</p>
            </div>
            <div class="message-body p-1">
                <div class="column is-full" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-easing="linear">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <div class="content">
                                <h6>個人診斷結果分析報告</h6>
                                <p>提供你已經完成的診斷結果分析報告，包含：</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>職業興趣診斷分析</li>
                                    <li>職場共通職能診斷分析</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-full" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-easing="linear">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <div class="content">
                                <h6>歷次診斷結果</h6>
                                <p>提供你已經完成的各項診斷結果，包含：</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>職業興趣探索結果</li>
                                    <li>職場共通職能診斷結果</li>
                                    <li>專業職能診斷結果</li>
                                    <li>結果總表</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="message">
            <div class="message-header">
                <p>諮詢服務與紀錄</p>
            </div>
            <div class="message-body p-1">
                <div class="column is-full" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-easing="linear">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <div class="content">
                                <h6>諮詢服務</h6>
                                <p>提供你向「本校師長」、「系統管理人員」提出問題</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-full" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-easing="linear">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <div class="content">
                                <h6>諮詢紀錄</h6>
                                <p>透過諮詢紀錄，查詢您所提出的各式問題及輔導諮詢人員針對問題所回覆的內容記錄</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

